<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Deleting pages">
    <p>All project members can delete any page in their project. To do so, simply navigate to the page you want to delete and click the "Delete" button in the grey toolbar at the top and bottom of the page.</p>
    <screenshot src="resources/images/delete_page.png"/>
    <note>
      <bullets>
          <item>The Overview page cannot be deleted.</item>
          <item>Pages cannot be deleted in edit mode.</item>
      </bullets>  
    </note>  
</topic>
